file.name: 3-parameters.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.1
info:
  version: 1.0.0
  title: Test API 3 - Parameters
servers:
- url: https://petstore.com
paths:
  "/pets/{category}":
    post:
      description: List all pets in a category
      operationId: addPet
      parameters:
      - in: path
        name: category
        required: true
        description: Pet category
        schema:
          type: string
          default: all
      - in: query
        name: limit
        description: Amt returned
        schema:
          type: integer
          format: int32
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Successful response
      requestBody:
        required: true
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              type: object
              required: ['search']
              properties:
                search:
                  type: string
                  description: Search pet details
                strict:
                  type: boolean
                  description: Exact matches?
              additionalProperties: true
